s: Córdoba guitars are designed in the Spanish tradition — resonant, lightweight and handmade. Varying from 1/4 to full size and with many color, tonewood, style and cutaway/electric options, your dream nylon string guitar is just a click away.
Córdoba Classical Guitars. Deeper body depth. Wider necks (52mm / 1.26") with high action. Enhanced sustain with a soft, long attack.

Córdoba seeks to guide the evolution of the nylon string guitar, blending traditional craftsmanship of the early master luthiers with modern developments. Every Córdoba is lightweight, responsive, and a direct descendant of the Spanish tradition.
Córdoba Thin Body Guitars. Body depth of less than 3", which helps reduce feedback. Perfect for live gigging!
We seek to guide the evolution of the nylon string guitar, blending traditional craftsmanship with modern developments.
Córdoba Crossover Guitars. The feel of steel string or electric guitar necks. Featuring a 48mm nut width, rounded neck profile and a curved radiused fingerboard.
